            <p class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-300 mb-2">La recette d'un bon prompt :</p>
            <div class="space-y-1.5 text-xs text-slate-400">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 font-bold">1.</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Quoi</strong> — ce que tu veux construire</span></div>
              <div class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-purple-400 shrink-0 font-bold">2.</span> <span><strong class="text-white">Où</strong> — le fichier, la page, la route concernée</span></div>
